"}],["$","p",null,{"children":["You don't. ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"You have an operational throughput problem."}]]}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Your practice is producing more than your back office can clean up. And the more you grow, the wider the gap gets. Here's what it looks like in real numbers, in a typical 3-doctor dental practice:"}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"bts-list","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"Claims submitted with at least one error"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"stat","children":"25-30%"}]]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"Recoverable AR sitting past 90 days"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"stat","children":"$$8-15k"}]]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"Monthly production lost to unfilled hygiene"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"stat","children":"$$3-5k"}]]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"Front desk time spent on verification calls"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"stat","children":"15-25 hrs/wk"}]]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"Treatment plans lost to coverage confusion"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"stat","children":"12-18%"}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"insight fade-in","style":{"marginTop":48},"children":["That's not a staffing problem you fix by posting on Indeed. ",["$","em",null,{"children":"That's an operational layer your practice is missing."}]]}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"block","id":"solution","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"solution-card fade-in","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"solution-glow"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"eyebrow","style":{"color":"var(--signal)"},"children":"— Our model"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"display","style":{"marginTop":20},"children":["We don't replace your team. ",["$","em",null,{"children":"We're the back office your team has been begging for."}]]}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Hired Billing Support gives you a dental-trained remote operations team that lives inside your practice management software. Same usernames. Same workflows. Same SOPs. They show up Monday morning ready to verify, bill, follow up, and close claims — and they don't take PTO during your busiest week."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"You'll have specific people assigned to your account. They'll learn your codes, your PPO contracts, your providers, your patients' names. They'll feel like staff — because operationally, they are."}],["$","p",null,{"style":{"fontFamily":"var(--serif)","fontStyle":"italic","fontSize":22,"color":"var(--paper)","marginTop":32,"maxWidth":680},"children":"The difference: you didn't have to hire them, train them for six months, or watch them leave for $4 more an hour."}]]}]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"block","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"block-head fade-in","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"eyebrow","children":"What we run for your practice"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"display","children":["The full dental operational ",["$","em",null,{"children":"stack."}]]}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Pick the layers you need. Run one service, or hand us the entire back office."}]]}],["$","table",null,{"className":"svc-table fade-in","children":["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"Insurance verification"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"Full breakdown of benefits 48 hours before the appointment. Maximums, deductibles, frequency limits, downgrades, missing tooth clauses, waiting periods — all documented in the chart before they sit down."}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"Eligibility & estimates"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"Real, accurate treatment estimates at presentation. No more \"we'll call you\" — patients accept treatment the same day."}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"child